(34810, 109859, 0, 1, '60年代(現場版)', '', '2011-04-17 00:00:00', 2000, 0, 2, 1, 'There was a guy called Johnny \r\nfrom a place called New Jersey \r\nHe didn’t want to stay with his mommy \r\nSo he took off in his black leather jacket \r\nHis mama said : “Where are you going?” \r\nHe said : “I’m going back to the 60’s.” \r\n \r\nso when he went back to the 60''s \r\nhe saw Sam, Frank, D.D. and Clamie \r\nthey told him that you''ve got a perfect mommy \r\nso you should go back to the 90''s \r\nhe said: “I don''t care about the 90’s, I just wanna live in the 60''s.”\r\n \r\n* 活在60’s的人們\r\n 是每一個人心中的神\r\n 是我們造就了你們\r\n 還是你們造就了我們\r\n 這就是活在60’s的人們\r\n \r\nwell, she wanted to find her little boy \r\nso she asked a guy called Tommy \r\nshe said : “Where can I find my little Johnny?” \r\nHe said : 「廢話，我們本來就活在60年代。」\r\n \r\nrepeat* \r\n\r\nsolo   \r\n\r\n*活在60’s的人們\r\n 是每一個人心中的神\r\n 是我們造就了你們\r\n 還是你們造就了我們\r\n 這就是活在60’s的~~hoo\r\n  這就是活在60’s的~~hoo\r\n  這就是活在60’s的\r\n 這就是活在60’s的人們\r\n', '', 187, '', 'Sam、Frankie', 'Sam', '', '', '', 0, 0, 1, '2011-04-17 14:19:01', '2013-10-07 17:18:30', '0000-00-00 00:00:00'),
